## Test Case ID: TC-CERT-002
Title: Verify certification reminders between 7–180 days before expiration
Related Ticket: UAC-2
Preconditions: Proxy as FT or PT worker; cert expiry exists in Workday
## Steps:
  1. Proxy login as worker in Workday
  2. Check notification section
  3. Validate if reminder alert appears between 7–180 days
## Expected Result:
  - Reminder alert is visible in notifications
  - Alert links to certification details or action page
